data.description: ***Seller officering $10k for interest rate buy down or closing costs*** All new high E windows, band new main level HVAC-2020*** This wonderfully updated home features gleaming hardwood floors, updated kitchen with newer stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, and brand new tile backsplash. Located on a cul-de-sac, this home also features a sunroom with deck and a very large fenced in yard. New light fixtures throughout. Fully finished basement has its own entrance, 5th bedroom (NTC - window), and full bathroom with shower. Main level office too! Call or email today to schedule your showing!
